WEBVTT

1
00:32:17.310 --> 00:32:19.310 
我绝不和它分离
I'll never part with it.

2
00:32:19.480 --> 00:32:23.770 
它曾让她想起我 今后也会让我想起她
It reminded her of me. It will remind me of her. Always.

3
00:32:24.190 --> 00:32:26.730 
我死时也要让这幅画挂在床头
I'll die with this picture above my bed.

4
00:32:27.070 --> 00:32:29.070 
看出相似之处了吗
See the resemblance?

5
00:32:30.070 --> 00:32:32.070 
是的
Oh, yes.

6
00:32:37.370 --> 00:32:39.120 
其实我们应该卖了它
Actually, we should sell it.

7
00:32:39.330 --> 00:32:42.330 
最好赶紧卖 以防他们偷回去
Sooner rather than later, in case they try to steal it back.

8
00:32:42.500 --> 00:32:43.380 
另外
Plus, something about

9
00:32:43.380 --> 00:32:45.250 
列车上的那群疯子士兵不太对劲
those lunatic foot-soldiers on the express...

